INSERT INTO items
    (item_name, description, img_src, price, brand, color_id)
VALUES
    ('Wayfair Basics® Pillow Insert', 'You found your favorite throw pillow, now fill it out with this essential pillow insert! Made from super-soft polyester microfiber, the shell sports a clean white finish. Designed to fit most standard pillow sizes, this insert is stuffed with a polyfill to a 4" thickness so your pillow will stay plump and keep its shape. Designed for universal use, these pillows are hypoallergenic for sensitive sleepers, and machine washable and dryer-safe for effortless upkeep.', 'wayfair_basics_pillow_insert.jpeg', 8, 'Wayfair Basics', 4),
    ('Evita 23" Table Lamp', 'Space-conscious and lightweight while still delivering style and illumination, it''s hard not to fall in love with table lamps. Take this one for example: With its slim pole and trumpet-shaped base, it''s a dash of modern-inspired style in almost any room. Featuring a minimalist silhouette, this piece puts all its focus on the Japanese paper hardback drum shade with a horizontal pattern. Perfectly sized to join an end table.', 'evita_23_table_lamp.jpeg', 115, 'AllModern', 4),
    ('3 Piece Dima Modern & Contemporary Mirror Set (Set of 3)', 'This trio of diamond shaped mirrors were inspired by the argyle patterns and can be hung separately, or in a variety of patterns. Each mirror measures 11¼ x 7 x 1/2 inch ( 28.5 x 18 x 1 cm) and hangs on a 15-inch (38 cm) chain. Sold as a set of three and includes all mounting hardware. The hardware itself is part of the decor as the mirrors hang on a chain secured to the wall by a rounded knob, which looks like a charming button.', '3_piece_dima_mirror_set.jpeg', 42, 'Umbra', 4),
    ('Delana Floral Red/Cream/Gray Area Rug', 'From the stunningly contemporary colors and the soft tones, this area rug is beautifully detailed in every way. This area rug is naturally soil, stain and fade resistant. Due to the difference of monitor colors, some rug colors may vary slightly.', 'delana_floral_mirror_set.jpeg', 70, 'Orren Ellis', 1),
    ('Ariel 19" Black Tripod Table Lamp', 'This Tripod Table Lamp is a contemporary piece that will brighten any office or desk space you place it in. With its wood legs and light gray linen lampshade, its simplistic yet functional design makes it a great piece. It effortlessly complements any office or living space.', 'ariel_19_black_tripod_lamp.jpeg', 48, 'Mercury Row', 3)

INSERT INTO items
    (item_name, description, img_src, price, brand, color_id)
VALUES
    ('Bohemian Blue 01 Landscape by Lisa Audit - Painting on Canvas', 'Our canvases are certified museum-grade and designed to withstand the test of time. Durability, image clarity, and color accuracy are our top priority, as we use archival inks to prevent fading and to preserve as much fine detail as possible with no over-saturation or color shifting. Featuring a proprietary design, these canvases produce the tightest corners without any bubbles, ripples, or bumps, and will not warp or sag over time. Additionally, our canvases include a finished backing with pre-installed hanging hardware that adds an extra level of style. Choose with or without a floating frame to achieve your desired look. This giclee wall art is sure to become the focal piece of your living room, family room, great room, bedroom, bathroom, office, kitchen, dining room, game room, bar, or more!
    ', 'bohemian_landscape_painting.jpg', 40, 'Gracie Oaks', 2),
    ('69" W x 70" H Williamsport Tribal Bohemian Feathers and Beads on Thread Graphic Pattern Native American Art Single Shower Curtain', 'Shower curtain is printed on 100% woven polyester construction for maximum strength. No liner needed. Exclusive design
    ', 'williamsport_tribal_shower_curtain.jpg', 50, 'Dakota Fields', 3),
    ('Odette 3 - Light Dimmable Sand Black Vanity Light', 'Bathroom remodels come in many forms, but across all of them, one thing remains the same: lighting matters. Layers of lighting turn tiny washrooms into statement-makers and large-scale bathrooms into spa sanctuaries. Take this vanity light, for example, the perfect pick for any industrial design or modern farmhouse style abode, it features a circular backplate and pipe-inspired arm made from metal awash in back finish.
    ', 'ordette_vanity_lights.jpg', 110, 'Industrial Lodge Home', 3),
    ('Boy Giraffe Contemporary Wall Décor', 'Indoor or outdoor aluminum artwork prints will add a special touch to your kitchen, bath, front door, outdoor patio or any special place. Rust and fade resistant. Aluminum print with hanging rope. Rounded corners.
    ', 'boy_giraffe_wall_decor.jpg', 15, 'Zoomie Kids', 2),
    ('Candy Red 3 Piece Contemporary Squares Wall Décor Set', 'Showcase your creativity by creating abstract patterns on your walls with these contemporary squares wall decor! These squares are uniquely designed with a cutout square in the middle which makes them look more stylish as room decor. Each set of these contemporary squares give you three squares of different sizes. These squares come in different colors so you can easily mix and match them and create beautiful patterns in your room. These squares can also be easily mixed and matched with another wall decor so you can easily channel your creativity through your walls! Get your own contemporary squares wall decor now!
    ', '3_piece_squares_wall_decor_set.jpg', 90, 'Ivy Bronx', 1),
    ('Gold 3 Piece Star Wall Decor Set', 'Liven up any wall with this set of 3 modern style gold starburst wall decor sculptures. Made of strong yet lightweight tin wire, each metal wall art piece has several straight, multiple-sized wire arms jutting out from the center, creating a 3D wall decor orb. The 3 sizes create stylish dimension any way you choose to hang them, all unified by their rich metallic gold finishes. This item ships in one carton. Items are ready to hang by keyhole slots in the back. Suitable for indoor use only. This set includes 3 wall décor. Contemporary design.
    ', '3_piece_star_wall_decor_set.jpg', 60, 'CosmoLiving by Cosmopolitan', 11),
    ('Bulverde Flatweave Gray Indoor / Outdoor Area Rug', 'Upgrade your lifestyle with the rich, textural appeal of an area rug. This easy-care, flatweave rug is elegant enough for your living room, bedroom, dining room, or family room, yet durable enough to enjoy outdoors on your porch, patio, poolside, or deck! Choose from a spectrum of versatile neutrals and fresh, decorator colors that display exciting variations thanks to the space-dyed, striated yarns.
    ', 'bulverde_flatweave_area_rug.jpg', 60, 'Zipcode Design™', 4),
    ('Angeline Cherry Red Area Rug', 'Bring a bold burst of color to your space with this cherry red area rug! This area rug is power-loomed from stain- and fade-resistant polypropylene in a shaggy 1" pile – perfect for rolling out in fashionable living rooms or digging your toes in right out of bed in the morning. Easily vacuumed or spot cleaned for effortless upkeep, this rug performs best when paired with a product pad to prevent shifting and sliding underfoot.
    ', 'angeline_area_rug.jpg', 30, 'Ebern Designs', 1),
    ('Chrome 4 Piece Kitchen Canister Set', 'This 4 Piece Kitchen Canister Set food storage container with air tight lid, and locking clamp, stainless steel.
    ', '4_piece_kitchen_canister_set.jpg', 59, 'Rebrilliant', 10),
    ('Black Caron 20" Cotton Napkin (Set of 4)', 'From everyday meals with the family to dinner parties with friends, small touches to the tablescape make all the difference. Dress up your culinary concoctions with this set of four napkins, perfect for adding that finishing touch to your dining decor. Crafted from cotton, they showcase a solid hue that pairs well with a variety of ensembles. When the meal is over, we recommend that you machine wash these pieces in cold water and then tumble dry low.
    ', 'caron_cotton_napkin_set.jpg', 25, 'Lark Manor™', 10)

INSERT INTO items
    (item_name, description, img_src, price, brand, color_id)
VALUES
    ('Red Revolve Sitting French Bulldog Figurine', 'Brimming with fashion-forward flair, this sculpture is sure to grab glances (and compliments!) in any arrangement. This statement piece showcases the silhouette of a bulldog with perky ears. It can easily fit atop any table, shelf, or desk in your home or office. A finish rounds out the design with even more modern appeal.
    ', 'revolve_bulldog_figurine.jpg', 35, 'Hashtag Home', 1),
    ('1.5" H x 16.25" W x 11.25" L Rectangular Serving Tray', 'Large enough for a multitude of uses, the stoneware serving platter features ridged edges that slope upward to contain food, while two wide handles are cut into each end to ensure a steady grip when carrying heavier foods like roasts or poultry to the table.
    ', 'rectangular_serving_tray.jpg', 70, 'Le Creuset', 4),
    ('Lehigh Wall Clock', 'Defined by its decorative gears and Roman numerals, this versatile wall clock is an even mix of classic and contemporary elements. Its rustic iron finish offers a nod to industrial style and blends with a variety of color palettes, while the gold metallic finish on its spade-style hands creates crisp contrast. This budget-friendly piece strikes a 15.5" circular silhouette that grabs glances without overwhelming your arrangement, and it''s set in an open, lightweight resin frame that makes hanging a breeze. Using a quartz movement operating mechanism, it requires one AA battery to operate (not included).'
    , 'lehigh_wall_clock.jpg', 42, 'Trent Austin Design®', 3),
    ('Argie Hello Coffee Barn Wood Box Sign', 'Designed and produced deliberately with a distressed appearance to give a vintage feel. Indoor use, a wonderful piece to fit for decoration of bar, restaurant, pub, home... Freestanding wood box sign, perfect for a gift.
    ', 'hello_coffee_wood_sign.jpg', 15, 'Winston Porter', 11),
    ('Gray Beals 18" Cotton Napkin (Set of 6)', 'Make casual home meals feel fancy, or impress guests at dinner parties with this set of napkins. They''re handmade in India from 100% cotton and feature a breezy striped design of white and your choice of complementary color. We love how the colored stripes have a chevron stitch pattern for a retro appeal. When dinner is finished, all you have to do is toss these napkins in the wash for a fuss-free clean. And if you need a crisp edge, they''re safe to iron too. Sold in sets of six.
    ', 'beals_cotton_napkin_set.jpg', 46, 'Sand & Stable™', 10),
    ('Depp Serving Tray', 'Add rustic farmhouse charm to your kitchen island or dining space by adding this oblong galvanized metal tray, perfect for serving snacks, beverages, etc. The ear handles on either side offer portability. The tray is ideal to be used for the decorative purposes to create a perfect focal point in your home. Crafted from galvanized steel in the hue of gray, the tray is corrosion resistive.
    ', 'depp_serving_tray.jpg', 38, 'Gracie Oaks', 10),
    ('Boyland 4 Piece Storage Jar Set', '4 Piece Storage Jar Set, adds a stylish element to your kitchen with this sleek look. Each jar includes an air-tight, bamboo lid. Canisters are made of durable borosilicate glass.
    ', 'boyland_4_piece_storage_jar_set.jpg', 40, 'Rebrilliant', 11),
    ('Blue Cornelia 20" Cotton Napkin (Set of 4)', 'Casual, yet stylish at the same time, the Two-Tone Fringe Table Napkins are great for everyday meals, family gatherings, or casual entertaining. They’re highly versatile and are easy to fit within any table décor, adding a touch of whimsy with their fringed edges. Pair with the Fringe Table Runner for a coordinated look.
    ', 'cornelia_cotton_napkin_set.jpg', 30, 'Saro', 2),
    ('Ketcham Serving Tray', 'Need a convenient spot to stash your tableware or something to carry your stem wine glasses from the kitchen to the dining table? We have just the solution in mind: this braided serving tray. The wooden bottom provides a flat surface to balance delicate glass and porcelain from place to place. The combination of the twisted seagrass with the wood handles makes it an ideal centerpiece for your ottoman or coffee table. Something to consider: When your new decorative tray needs some freshening up, we recommend wiping it clean with a soft, damp cloth.
    ', 'ketcham_serving_tray.jpg', 80, 'Birch Lane™', 11),
    ('3 Piece Kitchen Canister Set', 'From coffee beans to loose nuts, there''s plenty that can find a home in a kitchen canister. And with a set of three like this, you can be sure they do it in an on-trend package. Perfect for a bohemian touch to your kitchen ensemble, this set is crafted from porcelain with a series of blue motifs for a patterned look on a shelf or counter. Lead and PTFE-free, these jars form an airtight seal when closed.
    ', '3_piece_kitchen_canister_set.jpg', 50, 'Bungalow Rose', 2)

INSERT INTO items
    (item_name, description, img_src, price, brand, color_id)
VALUES
    ('Bambloom 6-Piece Assorted Kitchen Utensil Set (Part number: HX-10219)', 'The wooden spoons for cooking consist of salad fork, soup ladle, strainer spoon, serving spoon, solid spatula, and slotted spatula, meet all cooking needs in the kitchen for frying cooking baking, and stirring.
    ', 'bambloom_6_piece_wooden_utensils_set.jpg', 30, 'Bambloom', 11),
    ('White Wood Wall Clock', 'Evoking train stations of yesteryear, this charming 24"" wood wall clock instantly elevates your decor ensemble. Its weathered details pair perfectly with vintaged advertisement prints and reclaimed teak furniture, while its round silhouette blends effortlessly into any casual ensemble. Add this piece to the living room to complement a charming coastal aesthetic, then pair it with wood plank wall decor and fish-pattern pillows for a cohesive display. Looking to craft a more dynamic look? Pair this option with a sunburst mirror and an abstract canvas print for a statement-making arrangement, then round out the look with a hand-woven trellis rug for a pop of pattern.
    ', 'white_wood_wall_clock.jpg', 80, 'Beachcrest Home™', 10),
    ('Ceramic 0.72 qt. Storage Jar (Set of 4)', 'The practical and attractive bowls are made of ceramic and natural bamboo, with a nice look and compact size that holds more of your favorite spices and condiments. Widely used at home, hotel, cafe, buffet, the party serving for sugar, salt, spice, seasoning, pepper, corn starch, and chicken broth powder, and more. Can be used to store just about any spices or condiments to keep fresh and ready to use. The condiment jars also each come with ceramic spoons bamboo lids.
    ', 'ceramic_storage_jar.jpg', 35, 'Dakota Fields', 4),
    ('Metal Utensil Crock', '’Gather Cook Eat’ metal utensil crock holder, isn''t it annoying to have to rummage through drawers searching for the utensils you need while cooking? Our large rustic farmhouse utensil crock is a decorative and convenient solution for storing all of your cooking necessities easily at hand. Organize and display your everyday kitchen tools like spatulas, whisks, and knives with this countertop kitchen utensil caddy. It’s perfect to organize your kitchen so you won’t have to rummage through drawers while cooking.
    ', 'metal_utensil_crock.jpg', 18, 'Gracie Oaks', 4),
    ('Sequoia 4 Piece Cotton Napkin Set (Set of 4)', 'Set the scene for supper with our handwoven cotton Ikat napkins in flame stitch design. Generously sized for total lap protection, they also double as tea towels, so consider buying extra sets to coordinate your kitchen and table.
    ', 'sequoia_4_piece_napkin_set.jpg', 40, 'Pine Cone Hill', 6),
    ('Ballwin Twist Rope Trays (Set of 2)', 'Embellished with thick, twisting jute rope handles fastened with gleaming metal, this pair of smooth mango wood serving trays melds rusticity with glamour.
    ', 'ballwin_twist_rope_trays.jpg', 86, 'Highland Dunes', 11),
    ('12" H x 12" W x 0.75" D Neutral Arrangement I by Emma Scarvey - Wrapped Canvas Painting', 'Elegantly emulating freshly plucked branches in a vase, this painting is perfect for providing a touch of botanical charm just about anywhere. Printed on artist quality canvas, this USA-made painting uses UV- and fade-resistant archival inks for a professional, gallery-worthy look that’s sure to turn heads and inspire compliments. Built to last, this piece features patented warp-resistant construction plus a solid matboard backing. Best of all, wall mounting hardware is included, so this piece is effortlessly easy to hang.
    ', 'neutral_arrangement_painting.jpg', 23, 'Sand & Stable™', 6),
    ('Spring Cotton Geometric Throw Pillow Cover', 'Double sided print, Faux down filling, blown and closed, Water and mildew proof', 'spring_geometric_throw_pillow_cover.jpg', 50, 'East Urban Home', 5),
    ('Crivello Geometric Yellow/Off-White Indoor / Outdoor Area Rug', 'Looks aside, area rugs help absorb and decrease noise as they soften the step of hardwood and tile flooring. Made in Belgium, this one is constructed from polypropylene, a synthetic material designed to stand up to muddy shoes in the entryway and the occasional spill under the kitchen table. It features a 0.01" pile height, making it the perfect pick for adding a plush stage setter that promotes coziness in the living room, bedroom, and beyond.
    ', 'crivello_geometric_area_rug.jpg', 40, 'Mercury Row®', 5),
    ('2 Piece Denell Cement Metal Table Vase Set (Set of 2)', 'This hand-crafted Geometric Table Vase offers an organic feel to your home. It adds texture and style through clean lines with a contemporary feel. This piece add a focal point to any space.​​
    ', '2_piece_cement_metal_table_vase_set.jpg', 60, 'Union Rustic', 10)

INSERT INTO items
    (item_name, description, img_src, price, brand, color_id)
VALUES
    ('Green Iron/Glass Lantern with Handle', 'Brighten your living space, indoors or outdoors, with a pop of vibrant blue and the shimmering shine of candlelight. This charming railroad-style candle lantern features a large handle and hinged door.
    ', 'iron_glass_lantern.jpg', 25, 'Breakwater Bay', 6),
    ('Abenamar Southwestern Machine Woven Taupe Indoor / Outdoor Area Rug', 'These outdoor rugs are exquisite in appearance, color and texture. Made with a proprietary construction process which blends a distinct pattern direction that is unique to the market. The braided-woven look is dense and extremely durable to withstand the harsh outdoor elements year round. Manufactured with 100% polypropylene fiber which is easy to clean, soil, stain and sun resistant making them the perfect choice for easy living and easy maintenance.
    ', 'abenamar_southwestern_woven_area_rug.jpg', 60, 'Union Rustic', 10),
    ('Navy Adamson What Happens on the Porch Stays on the Porch Indoor/Outdoor Throw Pillow', 'All of your guests will feel at home when greeted by this typography pillow. Great for on the front porch or inside your entryway. Designed and printed in the China, this pillow is sure to add joy to your space.
    ', 'what_happens_pillow.jpg', 40, 'Laurel Foundry Modern Farmhouse®', 1),
    ('Powell 15.38'' H Glass Outdoor Wall Lantern', 'Crafted from metal and glass, this 15.75 in Traditional 1-Light Outdoor Wall Lantern Light takes its cues from lights of yesteryear with accents like a dome top and shepherd''s crook finial. It is atrium styling with Beveled Clear Glass sides and roof. Its base is open for easy access of changing the single light bulb.
    ', 'powell_wall_lantern.jpg', 45, 'Laurel Foundry Modern Farmhouse®', 3),
    ('Black Butterfly Metal Garden Bench', 'This metal garden butterfly chair will be a beautiful addition to your balcony, patio, front porch or garden area. Butterfly chair will add a functional, elegant, focal point in your home or outdoor living space.
    ', 'butterfly_metal_garden_bench.jpg', 120, 'Hi-Line Gift Ltd.', 3),
    ('Kraatz Ikat Flatweave Navy Blue/Ivory Indoor / Outdoor Area Rug', 'Liven up any layout with this dynamic area rug, showcasing a botanical motif in navy blue and ivory hues for a pop of pattern. This design resists mold, mildew, and UV, so it’s equally suited to sit inside your home or outdoors. Wherever you decide to roll it out, we recommend you pair this piece with a rug pad for extra cushioning and traction underfoot. The manufacturer backs this product with a one-year warranty.
    ', 'kraatz_ikat_area_rug.jpg', 40, 'Ophelia & Co.', 2),
    ('Cottle Porch Swing', 'Swing into relaxation with the chair! This trendy Cottle Hanging Rope Swing Chair hammock is the perfect addition to your home, patio, or garden. It features a sturdy frame for durability with tasteful bohemian style for a casual-retro touch. When you’re ready to relax and unwind, hang it from any sturdy overhang to create a cozy resting spot. It’s versatile enough to function as hammock chair for lounging or to display as a unique centerpiece.
    ', 'cottle_porch_swing.jpg', 80, 'Dakota Fields', 4),
    ('Mariam Ivory Area Rug', 'Technique: Braided, Construction: Handmade, Material: Polypropylene, Location: Indoor / Outdoor Use', 'mariam_area_rug.jpg', 40, 'Sand & Stable™', 4),
    ('Rust/Yellow Briese Dragonfly Outdoor Wall Art', '"Different choices as a single, Outdoor safe, Beautiful metal dragonfly outdoor safe wall artMaterial: Metal, Product Care: Wipe clean with a dry cloth"', 'briese_dragonfly_wall_art.jpg', 65, 'Laurel Foundry Modern Farmhouse®', 6),
    ('Citrus Nerys Outdoor Rectangular Throw Pillow', 'Inspired by exotic destinations and eclectic bohemian style, this charismatic lumbar pillow brings a pop of panache to your porch swing, living room sofa, master suite bedding, and beyond.
    ', 'nerys_outdoor_throw_pillow.jpg', 45, 'Ivy Bronx', 8),
    ('Francisco Handmade Braided Beige/Multicolor Area Rug', 'More than anything else, area rugs are art for your floors: They create the mood of your decor, guide the layout of your furniture, and establish a color scheme to follow (or rebel against). A new rug can, and will, dramatically change a room – the fun part is picking the one you love! This one for example: is handwoven in a geometric pattern in a beige and yellow color palette. It is crafted from jute and cotton. To clean this piece, we recommend professional cleaning when needed.
    ', 'francisco_braided_area_rug.jpg', 80, 'Bungalow Rose', 4),
    ('Brylee Geometric Gray Indoor / Outdoor Area Rug', 'This stunning area rug is made with a proprietary construction process that blends a distinct pattern direction that is unique to the market. The braided look combines complementing colors for an artistic visual appearance. It is made with 100% polypropylene fiber which is easy to clean and is soil, stain, and sun resistant. It will withstand the harsh outdoor elements all year round making them the perfect choice for easy living and easy maintenance.
    ', 'brylee_geometric_area_rug.jpg', 50, 'AllModern', 10),
    ('Blue Outdoor 12" Lumbar Pillow (Set of 2)', 'Add a stylish and contemporary accent to your outdoor furniture with this set of two Outdoor 12" Lumbar Pillow.
    ', 'outdoor_lumbar_pillow.jpg', 48, 'Greendale Home Fashions', 2),
    ('Waupaca Market Clay Buddha Garden Decor Statue', 'An image of serenity and peace, the Buddha is venerated in Asian culture for its teachings in enlightenment. Now you can add tranquility to your garden or any meditative area in your home with this Buddha statue. The statue features a sitting Buddha whose head is propped on his right knee while possessing an amiable expression. Place this statue on your home and make guests feel welcome while adding a decorative element to your space. Made of kaolin clay with a weathered stone finish, this statue is eye-catching and will strike a fancy to your guests.
    ', 'waupaca_buddha_statue.jpg', 70, 'Dakota Fields', 10),
    ('Wall Decor', 'Add an artful touch – indoors or out – with this eye-catching piece of wall art! Crafted from metal, its curved, petal-inspired design is accented by diamonds with a distressed finish, with a floral medallion placed directly in the center to complete the look. Measuring 36'' H x 36'' W, it’s sure to grab glances, whether it ends up accenting an empty wall over the sofa or enhancing the character of the veranda.
    ', 'dakota_fields_wall_decor.jpg', 90, 'Dakota Fields', 11),
    ('Burnt Orange Ruark Cotton Indoor/Outdoor Use Geometric Throw Pillow', 'Bring a dash of chic style to any ensemble with this eye-catching pillow, featuring a bold geometric motif. Let a pair pop against neutral linen upholstery on your living room sofa, then complete the whole, comfy look with a wool throw blanket or complementing slipcover. Featuring a weather-resistant design, this pillow is a perfect pick for your porch or patio ensemble; let them bring a breezy touch to your all-weather wicker seating group on the veranda, or have it complete your sunny poolside Adirondack set in style. If you have little ones romping around, use this pillow as a cushion in the playroom, then effortlessly clean up spills during nap time.
    ', 'ruark_cotton_throw_pillow.jpg', 50, 'Beachcrest Home™', 1)

INSERT INTO items
    (item_name, description, img_src, price, brand, color_id)
VALUES
    ('Passing Through II - Painting', 'We love the cool, calm, and serene scene on this painting print. It features an artful and abstract design in muted hues of blue and gray that complement your coastal- or traditional-inspired decor. The square frame is made in the USA from plastic in a neutral finish of your choice, and it can be hung horizontally or vertically in the living room or bedroom. The giclee print is stretched across a beveled matte board to keep it in place. It''s also protected with a clear piece of a.plastic. Plus, this painting print comes with all the hardware you need for fuss-free mounting.
    ', 'passing_through_painting.jpg', 50, 'Mercury Row®', 10),
    ('Rhode Iron Orb 25" Table Lamp Set (Set of 2)', 'Instantly transform your space with stylish form and function, with this elegant and unique Rhode Iron Orb 25" Table Lamp. With a beautiful yet sturdy open design metal base and ivory shade, the lamps provide warm ambient lighting for your bedroom, living room, or home office. The lamps conveniently come with energy-saving replaceable LED lightbulbs. It''s a perfect matching 2-piece set that will add a modern rustic touch to the nightstands or end tables in any room!
    ', 'rhode_iron_orb_table_lamp_set.jpg', 45, 'Gracie Oaks', 3),
    ('10" H x 10" W x 10" D Gautreau Galenna Sculpture', 'This vintage-inspired decorative sculpture is inspired by the Tehachapi Loop – the famous spiral of a railroad running through Tehachapi Pass in California. This orb’s rustic metal frame has a series of overlapping circles, and is finished in a black hue with an antique bronze finish where the loops join. It''s just the right finishing touch for your living room shelves, an entryway console, and any other space that calls for a little something extra.
    ', 'gautreau_galenna_sculpture.jpg', 50, 'Williston Forge', 11),
    ('Cream Square Velvet Pillow Cover (Set of 2)', 'The solid throw pillow covers bring the style of simplicity and the stripes on the pillow cover make it dainty and pretty. The velvet fabric gives softness and comfort while touching. Hope the pillow cover will bring you comfort wherever you go.
    ', 'square_velvet_pillow_cover.jpg', 40, 'Topfinel', 4),
    ('House Bookends (Set of 2)', 'Add charming rustic decorative accent and creative functional storage for any home or office setting with these reclaimed style house-shaped wood decorative bookends. These eye-catching rustic bookends are perfect for displaying books, magazines, file folders, and documents upright on any desk, table, shelf, or countertop, with 8 bottom foot pads to prevent scratches to their surfaces. For a convenient way to add functional organization and intriguing country-themed decoration to any home or office environment, these house-shaped wooden bookends are an excellent choice.
    ', 'house_bookends.jpg', 50, 'Gracie Oaks', 11),
    ('White Lia Rectangular Polyester Non-Slip Solid Bath Rug', 'Instantly upgrade your bathroom ensemble with this shaggy memory foam bath rug. Crafted of super-soft polyester chenille in a fashionable solid hue, this rug features a thick shag pile for a touch of texture, while a non-slip rubber backing helps prevent shifting and sliding underfoot. Inside, a plush memory foam core molds to the contours of your feet for comfort and support. Measuring 24"" W x 60"" L overall, this rug can be machine washed and tumble dried for fuss-free upkeep.
    ', 'lia_rectangular_solid_bath_rug.jpeg', 60, 'Zipcode Design™', 10),
    ('Benaiah Magnet Wall Hook', 'Keep oven mitts, cooking utensils, and other handy hanging kitchen gadgets in easy reach with this magnetic wall hook! Crafted from engineered wood, it showcases a white base and three light yellow wood posts that let you easily keep a favorite spatula on hand. Plus, since it features a magnetic mount, it''s easily added to refrigerators, metal posts, and more for flexible attachment. Measuring just 2'' H x 6.5'' W x 1.6'' D, this petite piece is perfect for spaces of all sizes.
    ', 'benaiah_magnet_wall_hook.jpg', 40, 'George Oliver', 4),
    ('Bath Towels', 'Gray cotton washcloth towel set of 10', 'reagan_10_piece_cotton_washcloth_towel_set.jpeg', 25, 'Eider & Ivory™', 10),
    ('Espresso Chet 14.5'' W x 54.5'' H x 13'' D Solid Wood Linen Cabinet', 'Linen towers like this one combine handy storage and a space-conscious design to deliver one of our favorite organizational win-wins! This tower is crafted from bamboo, and features three exposed shelves and one behind its louvered door, so there''s space to stow everything from an extra roll (or two) of bath tissue to soaps and lotions. Plus, thanks to its breeze slatted design and clean-lined silhouette, it''s perfect for a modern, spa-like feel. This tower measures 54.5'' H x 14.5'' W x 13'' D, making it a slim option easily slipped into an unused powder room corner.
    ', 'chet_solid_wood_linen_cabinet.jpg', 120, 'Dotted Line™', 11),
